<!--
  Every user-facing string in the settings slice (PRD §6.10: English-first, string infrastructure
  ready from day one). Copy is written from the couch (PRD §8.6): controls say what they do, in the
  active voice, and no system jargon reaches the screen — "Keep history for", never "Retention
  policy"; "Storage format", never "schema version".
-->
